## Multi Search

```elixir
search_results =
  Req.new(
    base_url: "http://localhost:7700",
    auth: {:bearer, search_key}
  )
  |> Req.post!(
    url: "/multi-search",
    json: %{
      queries: [
        %{
          indexUid: "blog-posts",
          q: "com",
          attributesToHighlight: ["*"],
          highlightPreTag: "<yay>",
          highlightPostTag: "</yay>",
          showRankingScore: true
        },
        %{
          indexUid: "blog-tags",
          q: "cli",
          attributesToHighlight: ["*"],
          highlightPreTag: "<yay>",
          highlightPostTag: "</yay>",
          limit: 2
        },
        %{
          indexUid: "blog-authors",
          q: "derpy",
          attributesToHighlight: ["*"],
          highlightPreTag: "<yay>",
          highlightPostTag: "</yay>",
          limit: 2
        }
      ]
    }
  )
```

